HEADWORD: Papular
<hw>Pap"u*lar</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Covered
with papules.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>Consisting of papules;
characterized by the presence of papules; <as>as, a <ex>papular</ex>
eruption</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Papule</ent>⟦br⟧
